      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Time for the WATC Derby now where SENTIMENTAL LEGEND (2) looks the one to beat coming through the Melvista. He meets ABERDEEN FLYER worse at the weights here, but the draw should see him right on the speed and Pike hops back on board. Can raise the bar again and win the Derby. ABERDEEN FLYER (1) was too good in the Roberts before ending up way back in the pack in the Melvista, closing strongly in the process. Gets a weight swing in his favour now, though where he gets to from the barrier is the query. WONDERFULLY MADE (7) bolted in to win the Oaks 10 days ago in a romp. The time was slower there against the boys, but she's already ticked the 2400m box impressively. Can be handy and make her presence felt. Chris Parnham rides MASMELO (8) over ABERDEEN FLYER and that's a good push for her chances. Keep safe. WYNN LAS VEGAS (3) can lead and be in this for a long way.",
